#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga "
msgstr "1. Immersion "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Paṭhamasamaṇabrāhmaṇasutta "
msgstr "5. Ascetics and Brahmins (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.5:1.1"
msgid "“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhiṃsu, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhiṃsu. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, whatever ascetics and brahmins truly wake up—in the past, "

msgctxt "sn56.5:1.2"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhissanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhissanti. "
msgstr "future, "

msgctxt "sn56.5:1.3"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhanti. "
msgstr "or present—all of them truly wake up to the four noble truths. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.417, sc2
msgctxt "sn56.5:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn56.5:2.2"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ … pe … dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ. "
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. … "

msgctxt "sn56.5:2.3"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhiṃsu … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.5:2.4"
msgid "abhisambojjhissanti … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.5:2.5"
msgid "abhisambojjhanti, sabbe te imāni cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhanti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.5:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.5:3.2"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
